casebody.data:
Samuel POPKOFF, Appellant,
v.
EXTRA SPACE MANAGEMENT, INC., Respondent. Motion No: 2019-287 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided May 9, 2019

Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that this Court does not **738have jurisdiction to entertain this motion for leave to appeal from the order of the Appellate Division entered in this action commenced in the Civil Court of the City of New York (see NY Const, art VI, § 3 [b][7]; CPLR 5602[a] ).
